00:54:33.110 --> 00:54:35.870
So resources we grow
inside ourselves

00:54:35.870 --> 00:54:41.070
help us accept and be
with and bear our pain,

00:54:41.070 --> 00:54:42.900
including the pain
that lands when we are

00:54:42.900 --> 00:54:44.600
compassionate for other people.

00:54:44.600 --> 00:54:47.090
So resources, growing
resources, in part,

00:54:47.090 --> 00:54:49.730
is a means to an end
of being able to be

00:54:49.730 --> 00:54:53.180
authentic and inclusive
about everything we feel.

00:54:53.180 --> 00:54:56.150
