00:55:18.260 --> 00:55:20.510
ourselves, we become
much more able to deal

00:55:20.510 --> 00:55:22.610
with the negative
things out in the world.

00:55:22.610 --> 00:55:26.610
We become more confident,
more courageous, spunky,

00:55:26.610 --> 00:55:29.750
you know, feisty, keep going.

00:55:29.750 --> 00:55:32.540
We're not going to be stopped,
because we have built up

00:55:32.540 --> 00:55:33.320
strengths inside.

00:55:33.320 --> 00:55:35.560
So to me, they really,
really work together.

